bf","tid":773722,"uid":35559,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T18:42:55.000Z","msg":"認真答：開水喉一路沖，沖到feel到無咁痛，跟住開盤水加冰落去浸住隻手，浸完仲痛就不停loop依兩個steps<br />\n<br />\n不過都過咗咁耐，你搽藥嘅話唔爭在斬埋隻手佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16fba9c1d39e42fbc3e56c655b7964d1bad46aef","tid":773722,"uid":127281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T18:43:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/10/024258_baf3845e4db3ba05140869fcaab1e4ef.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F10%2F024258_baf3845e4db3ba05140869fcaab1e4ef.png&h=3bb6eba3&s={SIZE}\" /> 紅色果到d皮甩晒"},{"pid":"f4d13553fd3b9925aba53bfa525d9c9f06ee1433","tid":773722,"uid":10453,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T18:45:05.000Z","msg":"點解揀浸冰水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">有些人覺得用水沖沒辦法快速降溫，會將患部泡冰水或用冰塊冰敷，不過直接用冰水或冰塊降溫可能會導致皮膚凍傷，因此還是應該使用「流動的水」，沖洗5至30分鐘，才是正確的方式。</code></pre>"},{"pid":"5a8685d944696021e9ba928640ea93d41dfd9b72","tid":773722,"uid":539,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T18:45:59.000Z","msg":"倒瀉麵辣親下都要上黎問真係好on9"},{"pid":"a97bdfa3b5da5845753abaa289e37eb095e978f0","tid":773722,"uid":127281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f647238e2504b84a46682e76b2cf99d53e4f76a2","tid":773722,"uid":127281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd73aedae98a65b74f42f53d7dcee95dd0786440","tid":773722,"uid":150852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T18:40:05.000Z","msg":"其實最好係沖室溫水<br />\n沖到唔痛<br />\n浸冰水好大機會會起水泡<br />\n基本上沖到唔痛就得<br />\n之後搽返d嘢痛幾日就冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw 建議樓主咁大個人可以google吓<br